  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK867">
<l>koṭuttuṅ koḷalvēṇṭu maṉṟa vaṭuttiruntu </l>
<l>māṇāta ceyvāṉ pakai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is indeed necessary to obtain even by purchase the hatred of him who having begun (a work) does what is not conductive (to its accomplishment).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
